{"tid":592913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【亞冠盃】鄭展龍世界波絕殺柏雷素爾 傑志獲亞冠盃首勝","createTime":"2018-03-14T14:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T05:25:11.000Z","uid":14719,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"df37d86bc4069488df5150d029bc0b87c9bab6af","tid":592913,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180314/large/1521037293_d8c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180314%2Flarge%2F1521037293_d8c8.jpg&h=19965685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賽後入球功臣鄭展龍受訪時直言，對於球隊贏波感到十分高興，多謝球隊的努力和朱Sir的賞識：「開心幫到球隊取勝，好重要的三分，亞冠盃是亞洲最高水平的球會賽事，能夠取得入球好高興。教練及隊友好信任我，由小到大是鼓勵有空位，有機會便要射門，從青年軍賽事便是這樣，感謝球迷入場支持。」鄭展龍續指：「我的強項是左右腳都能夠開弓，能夠取得入球感到十分高興。」當被問到教練賽前有否透露自己將會上陣，鄭展龍則稱：「自己一直做好出場準備，機會來到便要好好把握。」<br />\n<br />\n傑志教練朱志光則表示：「開心，取勝過程不容易，分組賽首兩場以大比數落敗，輸波後信心有少少動搖，過去兩場開始跟到這個水平的節奏，球隊今場防守高度集中，好貫徹，好開心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180314/57946091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57946091&d=tGUmkzaQjrZs4McMo98rlp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9dfc2b45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57946091&h=98604834\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180314/57946091</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/220753_8a975e915094652abb301d8cf705e636.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F220753_8a975e915094652abb301d8cf705e636.gif&h=42e38b0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7a8f45e21ecb2054a1434072edc1e6b7848530c","tid":592913,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":49,"score":-46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:16:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73dbc